Interface IJSONMapProcessor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractJSONMapProcessor, JSONMapsToJSONListProcessor

    public interface IJSONMapProcessor
    Interface for processing (possibly multi-page) lists of JSON objects.
    Author:
    Ruud Senden

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void notifyNextPage(PagingData pagingData)
      For multi-page requests, this method will be invoked before loading the next page.
      void process(JSONMap json)
      Allow implementations to process the current JSON object from a list of one or more JSON objects.

        void notifyNextPage(PagingData pagingData)
